1. grab bitcoin from the master branch off github
2. `cd bitcoin/depends`
3. Inside of the `bitcoin/depends` repo, run `make -j9`
4. `cd ..`
5. `./autogen.sh`
6. `./configure --prefix=$PWD/depends/arm-apple-darwin20.3.0`
7. `make -j9`
